### è‡ªåŠ¨åŒ–ç»´æŠ¤æµç¨‹

#### CI/CDé›†æˆç»´æŠ¤

```yaml
# .github/workflows/docs-maintenance.yml
name: Documentation Maintenance

on:
  schedule:
    # æ¯å‘¨ä¸€æ—©ä¸Š8ç‚¹æ‰§è¡Œç»´æŠ¤ä»»åŠ¡
    - cron: '0 8 * * 1'
  workflow_dispatch:

jobs:
  maintenance:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Update document versions
        run: node docs/scripts/update-doc-index.js --update-versions

      - name: Generate quality report
        run: node docs/scripts/generate-quality-report.js

      - name: Check expired documents
        run: node docs/scripts/validate-docs.js --check-expiry

      - name: Auto-fix minor issues
        run: node docs/scripts/fix-doc-metadata.js --force
